2 Fine-mapping results (maximum 1 causal)

Current set-up:

  • The 1000 Genome as a LD reference panel
    • Following the protocol from Paintor (all discordant SNPs are simply ignored)
  • The FINEMAP program with the maximum number of causals equal to 1
    • Not an optimal configuration. Results in picking SNPs with the top P-values (see figures below).
